very uncomfortable.

360
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:34,281
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

361
00:15:34,282 --> 00:15:35,499
Charlie, I've got
a problem.

362
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:36,517
How about that,

363
00:15:36,518 --> 00:15:38,319
the problem's got a problem.

364
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,970
