about Chris?

386
00:16:12,037 --> 00:16:13,787
I don't want to lose Lyndsey;
I love her.

387
00:16:13,788 --> 00:16:15,322
And I love
huevos rancheros

388
00:16:15,323 --> 00:16:18,008
and chocolate "felicidadas"
on my pillow.

389
00:16:18,009 --> 00:16:20,844
Okay, we seem to be talking
at cross purposes here.

390
00:16:20,845 --> 00:16:23,330
'Cause you're not focusing
on the real issue.

391
00:16:23,331 --> 00:16:25,666
I've just lost the best
housekeeper since...

392
00:16:25,667 --> 00:16:27,468
Wilma Flintstone.

393
00:16:29,521 --> 00:16:30,854
