409
00:17:22,107 --> 00:17:23,557
Come on in.

410
00:17:23,558 --> 00:17:25,276
Buenas noches, Señor Harper.

411
00:17:30,498 --> 00:17:32,366
Yeah, yeah, me, too.

412
00:17:33,601 --> 00:17:34,585
Esmerelda?

413
00:17:34,586 --> 00:17:37,404
Oh, como esta, Señor Alan?

414
00:17:37,405 --> 00:17:38,756
Muy bien.

415
00:17:38,757 --> 00:17:39,873
Charlie, what's going on?

416
00:17:39,874 --> 00:17:41,074
Excusez-moi.

417
00:17:43,111 --> 00:17:46,413
From now on, Berta will be
our day housekeeper

418
00:17:46,414 --> 00:17:48,716
